    <h2 class="ttl" id="why-ai-heading" style="color:#fff;max-width:820px;">Gmail, Outlook &amp; Yahoo <span style="color:var(--teal)">Use AI to Block Your Emails.</span> Favze Uses AI to Get Through.</h2>
    <p class="sub" style="margin-top:14px;">Without AI optimization, even well-written emails from Northern Indiana businesses land in spam — invisible to the customers who opted in to hear from you. Favze's AI-first approach ensures every campaign passes the algorithms that control inbox placement, engagement, and revenue.</p>

    <div class="why-ai-grid">

      <div class="why-ai-card">
        <div class="why-ai-watermark">01</div>
        <div class="why-ai-icon icon-i">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#0A89A3" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M2 8l10 7 10-7" stroke="#0A89A3" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
