        <h3>Inbox Placement is AI-Driven</h3>
        <p>Gmail, Outlook, and Yahoo Mail all use machine learning algorithms to decide if your email lands in the primary inbox, the promotions tab, or spam. Sender reputation, authentication (SPF, DKIM, DMARC), engagement history, and content signals all feed these models. Favze engineers every campaign to score high across all these signals — so your emails reach the subscribers who want them.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-ai-card">
        <div class="why-ai-watermark">02</div>
        <div class="why-ai-icon icon-y">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><polygon points="12,2 15,9 22,9 16,14 18,21 12,17 6,21 8,14 2,9 9,9" stroke="#ffb400" stroke-width="1.7" fill="none"/></svg>
