        <h3>Revenue-Focused Personalization</h3>
        <p>AI analyzes each subscriber's behavior, purchase history, and engagement patterns to determine exactly which offer to send them and when. Generic batch-and-blast emails generate low open rates and high unsubscribes. Personalized, behavior-triggered campaigns generate measurably higher clicks, conversions, and revenue per email — often 3–5x the results of untargeted sends.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-ai-card">
        <div class="why-ai-watermark">03</div>
        <div class="why-ai-icon icon-g">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="#34A853" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2" stroke="#34A853" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Optimal Send Time Prediction</h3>
        <p>AI predicts when each individual subscriber is most likely to open an email based on their historical open behavior. Sending at the wrong time — even with the right message — tanks open rates. Favze's send-time optimization ensures your campaigns hit inboxes at the exact moment each local customer is most likely to engage, driving materially higher open and click-through rates across your list.</p>
      </div>

