        <h3>Subject Line & Content Testing</h3>
        <p>AI tests subject lines, preview text, CTAs, image placement, and content structure — identifying combinations that generate the highest open and click-through rates for your specific audience. What works for a Goshen retail store is different from what works for a South Bend law firm. Favze uses platform-native AI testing tools to surface the highest-performing variables for your list.</p>
