        <h3>Email Fatigue Prevention</h3>
        <p>Sending too frequently to disengaged subscribers damages your sender reputation and inflates unsubscribe rates. AI monitors individual engagement patterns and automatically adjusts send frequency to keep your list healthy, your reputation clean, and your subscribers profitable over the long term — not just for one campaign cycle.</p>
