        <h3>Layout & CTA Optimization</h3>
        <p>Machine learning identifies which email layouts, button colors, CTA placements, and copy styles generate the most clicks and revenue for your audience. Favze applies these insights to every campaign — so each send is built on data from what your specific subscribers actually respond to, not generic best-practice assumptions from another industry or geography.</p>
