      <span class="lbl lbl-dark">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
      <h2 class="ttl ttl-dark" id="faq-heading" style="margin-top:6px;">Questions About Email Marketing in Northern Indiana</h2>
      <p class="sub sub-dark" style="margin:12px 0 48px;">Straight answers to what Elkhart County and Michiana business owners ask most — about strategy, deliverability, cross-client rendering, platforms, and everything in between.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;">

        <div class="fq-item" style="border-top:1.5px solid #ddd;border-bottom:1.5px solid #ddd;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
