          <div class="fq-ans" style="display:none;padding:0 0 20px;font-size:0.93rem;color:#555;line-height:1.78;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <div itemprop="text">AI-optimized email marketing uses machine learning to maximize inbox placement, engagement, and revenue from every campaign. Gmail, Outlook, and Yahoo Mail all use AI to decide which emails reach the primary inbox versus spam. Without AI optimization, even well-written emails from Northern Indiana businesses can miss the inbox entirely. Favze uses AI to optimize subject lines, send timing, content layout, and audience segmentation — so every campaign lands in front of the right local customers at the right moment.</div>
