          </button>
          <div class="fq-ans" style="display:none;padding:0 0 20px;font-size:0.93rem;color:#555;line-height:1.78;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <div itemprop="text">Yes — cross-client and cross-device compatibility is a core part of every Favze email campaign. Favze builds and tests every email template across Gmail (web, iOS app, Android app), Outlook 2016/2019/2021/365 (Windows and Mac), Apple Mail (iPhone, iPad, Mac), Yahoo Mail, Samsung Email, and all major mobile and desktop email clients before any campaign goes live. Emails are built with bulletproof table-based HTML structure, inline CSS, web-safe fallback fonts, fluid layouts that reflow correctly on any screen width, MSO conditional comments for Outlook rendering, and dark mode compatibility. Not a single penny of your email budget is wasted sending campaigns that break on specific devices or clients.</div>
