          </button>
          <div class="fq-ans" style="display:none;padding:0 0 20px;font-size:0.93rem;color:#555;line-height:1.78;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <div itemprop="text">Outlook on Windows uses Microsoft Word's rendering engine rather than a web browser, which means it does not support many standard CSS properties that work in Gmail or Apple Mail. Favze addresses this by building email templates with table-based HTML structure, MSO-specific conditional comments, VML-based background images for Outlook, bulletproof CSS buttons, and Outlook-specific fixes for line height, font rendering, and image spacing. Every campaign is tested in Outlook 2016, 2019, 2021, and Microsoft 365 on Windows and Mac before any send.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fq-item" style="border-bottom:1.5px solid #ddd;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
          <button class="fqb" type="button" aria-expanded="false" style="width:100%;background:none;border:none;text-align:left;padding:20px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:0.97rem;color:#0a0a0a;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px;font-family:var(--font-body);">
